Suggested installation method
=============================

OS Dependencies (Ubuntu package names):
	libgee-0.8-dev
	libgee-0.8-2
	valac-0.30 (or newer)

OS Optional Features
	gobject-introspection
	libgirepository
	libgladeui-dev

Python Required Packages
	meson

1) Install dependencies
	sudo apt install libgee-0.8-dev libgee-0.8-2 valac-0.30
	pip3 install --user meson
2) [OPTIONAL] Install additional packages
	sudo apt install gobject-introspection libgirepository libgladeui-dev
3) Build library and test projects
	meson build
	cd build
	ninja
4) Install to the system
	sudo ninja install
	
